00:07:38.770 --> 00:07:42.030
which means people can feel
dizzy, or actually faint,

00:07:42.030 --> 00:07:43.770
typically, when
they're standing up.

00:07:43.770 --> 00:07:45.720
Sometimes after meals.

00:07:45.720 --> 00:07:48.360
Another one is just
chronic fatigue--

00:07:48.360 --> 00:07:50.520
