00:10:05.690 --> 00:10:08.210
And the problem that
these patients have--

00:10:08.210 --> 00:10:11.780
the muscles are still there, but
what you can see in the slides

00:10:11.780 --> 00:10:14.060
from the top with
a healthy person

00:10:14.060 --> 00:10:16.550
is there are all these
axons, these nerve

00:10:16.550 --> 00:10:19.730
cells that come
running down, and they

00:10:19.730 --> 00:10:22.040
control the blood vessels.

00:10:22.040 --> 00:10:23.930
See this round
blood vessel here?

00:10:23.930 --> 00:10:26.420
The little yellow
squiggles are the nerves

00:10:26.420 --> 00:10:29.270
that tell the blood vessel
when to open and close.

00:10:29.270 --> 00:10:32.540
And what you can see is in
the slides from the bottom,

00:10:32.540 --> 00:10:35.600
there's far fewer nerves,
and the blood vessel

00:10:35.600 --> 00:10:36.650
is gaping open.

00:10:36.650 --> 00:10:40.460
So the point is that when
your nerves are messed up,

00:10:40.460 --> 00:10:42.440
they control the blood
vessels, your muscles

00:10:42.440 --> 00:10:44.870
may not get the
oxygen and nutrients

00:10:44.870 --> 00:10:46.220
they need to function.

00:10:46.220 --> 00:10:48.800
And in many people,
not all, that's

00:10:48.800 --> 00:10:50.990
why they can't get out
of bed in the morning

00:10:50.990 --> 00:10:53.640
when they have neuropathy.

00:10:53.640 --> 00:10:56.930
