00:48:22.950 --> 00:48:25.980
as kind of a restricted
form of these same--

00:48:25.980 --> 00:48:29.070
I'm pointing here because this
is the most common location

00:48:29.070 --> 00:48:30.930
where people get shingles--

00:48:30.930 --> 00:48:34.050
as a restricted form of
a small fiber neuropathy.

