00:51:12.770 --> 00:51:15.560
is your protocol, and what
happens to patients who are

00:51:15.560 --> 00:51:17.150
progressively getting worse?

00:51:17.150 --> 00:51:19.364
Would you repeat it soon?

00:51:19.364 --> 00:51:20.780
How do you observe
