01:09:47.720 --> 01:09:50.930
The good news is that there's
an upcoming meeting that

01:09:50.930 --> 01:09:53.240
will bring together
experts around the world

01:09:53.240 --> 01:09:57.290
to develop what's called a
consensus case definition.

01:09:57.290 --> 01:09:59.120
And when there's
a case definition,

01:09:59.120 --> 01:10:02.191
it's very, very helpful, even
though they're not perfect

01:10:02.191 --> 01:10:02.690
either.

01:10:02.690 --> 01:10:04.460
But at least what
it means is there's

01:10:04.460 --> 01:10:07.790
a mutually agreed upon
diagnostic standard

01:10:07.790 --> 01:10:10.620
as to who has it, and
who doesn't have it.

01:10:10.620 --> 01:10:14.600
So that's going to
be very helpful.

01:10:14.600 --> 01:10:28.720
Well, fibromyalgia-- if I
were a fibromyalgia patient,

01:10:28.720 --> 01:10:31.250
I think patients
want to get better.

01:10:31.250 --> 01:10:36.640
And when you have an illness
that is really a label--

01:10:36.640 --> 01:10:39.970
that's the key point, is
that fibromyalgia is not

01:10:39.970 --> 01:10:41.080
a diagnosis.

01:10:41.080 --> 01:10:42.710
It's a label.

01:10:42.710 --> 01:10:45.150
It's a word that we put on
a collection of symptoms.

01:10:45.150 --> 01:10:46.630
It doesn't have one cause.

01:10:46.630 --> 01:10:50.200
Those same symptoms
have different causes

01:10:50.200 --> 01:10:52.990
in different people,
and it's so important

01:10:52.990 --> 01:10:57.760
to move beyond the label, and
press your doctor to tell you

01:10:57.760 --> 01:11:00.460
what's the underlying
medical cause in you.

01:11:00.460 --> 01:11:03.580
And even if they might
not know it in 2017,

01:11:03.580 --> 01:11:07.150
maybe they could figure
it out in 2018, or 2019.

01:11:07.150 --> 01:11:10.480
So I think it's up to each
person with fibromyalgia.

01:11:10.480 --> 01:11:12.580
People have, unfortunately,
different levels

01:11:12.580 --> 01:11:13.990
of medical coverage.

01:11:13.990 --> 01:11:17.770
Some docs are more interested
in pursuing things than others.

01:11:20.440 --> 01:11:23.541
I know what I would do
if I were the patient.

