01:12:27.070 --> 01:12:30.100
Then it takes a while for
the nerve cells to regrow,

01:12:30.100 --> 01:12:32.560
and they may not even
regrow in everybody,

01:12:32.560 --> 01:12:35.650
and they may regrow at different
rates than somebody who's 15,

01:12:35.650 --> 01:12:37.960
than somebody who's 65.

01:12:37.960 --> 01:12:40.450
So as of now, the
skin biopsies are

01:12:40.450 --> 01:12:44.320
most helpful for initial
diagnosis, and their role

01:12:44.320 --> 01:12:46.090
